    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更新上线：季节庆典！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e5efd8247125f93615b31f370fb40bf2.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新季节特有的物品。颜值超高！等你收集！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e14cc8b9b78629d4d09937315e131be1.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >季节限定动物，一同上线！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e75ef8696ff2451bf55d3d159c5124f3.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=281 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/a1afab2e5a63db37a97e56350a7ca3d5.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>传说有一个世外桃源，风景秀丽、依山傍水，更有一棵古老的精灵之树，为这里带来风调雨顺。小动物们被古树的灵气所吸引，栖息于精灵之树下。<br><br>一日火山爆发，许多地方从此变成了荒芜。小动物们纷纷出动，决定恢复这里的生态环境，利用净化之光的力量，在此建设一个全新的美好家园。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合成带来快乐，治疗一切强迫症。</h2>三个一样的物品即可合成一个更高级的物品，这便是这个世界的基本法则。<br>将繁杂的物品统统合成，不断地收集与整理。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/41b13c9308a6a350840c59637b8ef4af.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >做好资源管理，为家园的资源循环努力。</h2>各种各样花草树木和产出资源的建筑，需要不断地合成以及规划。<br>生产和建造达成良性循环，不断壮大动物家园。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/2de2d47d330b2233fb7dc67bcad7f7c5.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种小动物可爱收集，助力采集好帮手。</h2>通过合成动物球，让小猫、小熊、小猴等得力助手，采集花果不在话下。<br>小动物们每次合成还能解锁新的服饰，以更可爱的样子穿梭于林间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/e39010e65b24b0370dcd87b18a7ce223.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精美建筑随心摆，外观党的DIY家园</h2>多达400块待解锁地块逐渐开放。<br>将各色精美的物品、建筑合成，按照你的心意摆放，美好家园等待你建造。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.poster.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.webm?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/ebdceb2a7b17462009479f0bcf012002.mp4?t=1754639774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超多收集内容，图鉴党肝不停！</h2>包含动物、植物、生产建筑等，多达200个多种类收集内容。<br>丰富的图鉴等待你来填满。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301850/extras/dd41448493060f55e6b8726db40e3184.avif?t=1754639774\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多玩法，还在路上。</h2>未来还会有怎样的新动物和新建筑呢？敬请期待~",
